        <div class="msgSubject">Minimap and other UI Annoyances</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-03 17:15:57   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1286147757113305303" id="quote-1286147757113305303" class="msgQuoteCheck"/><label for="quote-1286147757113305303"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=1286147757113305303&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1286147757113305303&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow" onclick="return multiQuote(this)">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1286147757113305303" onclick="followToggle('add','1286147757113305303')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
