      <div class="msgContentFrame">I have seen these issues as well, and I don't use those addons, so I think that rules them out.  <br /> <br />One other thing I notice with the map issue-every single time that I log in and the map is zoomed in, any quests I had been tracking are now not tracked. Achievements tracked will still be up, but not quests. And I haven't found a pattern to it yet either, sometimes it happens, sometimes it doesn't. Sometimes on my 80s, sometimes on my lower levels. Whether I logged out in a rested area, or out in the world.  <br /> <br />The loot lag I also notice with the bags you get as a reward from the Argent Tournament. Sometimes that 10g just sits there and stares at you, sometimes the bag will close back up and I have to click it again to get the money out. I just chalk it up to &quot;loot lag&quot; which just happens *I guess* from the delay, however minimal, between your computer and theirs.  <br /> <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm"> <br />14 level 80s  <br />ZERO heroic dungeons EVER <br />and No heirlooms and no RecruitaFriend <br /></span> <br /></div></div>
